Author: René Bertin <rjvbertin@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Feb 18 16:34:57 2026 +0100

    Add a menu for selection which I/O engine fio should use
    
    This is populated dynamically as a function of the platform
    we're running on, but the last used value is store in the prefs.
    Also show the selected engine in the title, and in the saved output.
    
    Committed from host : Bola

